    <script type="text/javascript">
        function display(i,j){
            var k=i+j;
            alert ('The value of k is'+k)
        }
    </script>
    <h2>If you want k Value just click the submit button</h2>
    <center><input type="button" value="submit" onclick="display(10,20)"/></center>
</body>
</html>


Result:
-------
It gives the k value with pop-up or alert message


